personajes.name: My Melody
personajes.description: My Melody loves to bake cookies with her mom! And also, she plays the flute. Her cutepink hood was handmade!

personajes.name: Hello Kitty
personajes.description: Hello Kitty was born in the suburbs of London. Her hobbies include baking cookies and making new friends. As she always says, you can never have too many friends!

personajes.name: Kuromy
personajes.description: Kuromi keeps a secret diary and loves romance novels! Her favourite color is blackand she is the leader of a biker band.

personajes.name: cinammoroll
personajes.description: Cinnammoroll is actually a chubby dog! He loves soft and warm cinnamon rolls and has looong ears that help him fly.

personajes.name: Little Twin
personajes.description: Kiki, and Lala. They love staying in clouds and stars! Very adventurous and very curious. Love a good chat.

personajes.name: Keroppi
personajes.description: Keroppi is a profesional trumpet player, who also enjoys baseball and spending time with his family. He's always with a smile in his face!

personajes.name: Pochacco
personajes.description: Pochacco's favourite icecream is banana flavoured! He loves when its spring so he can skateboard all day, sadly he's a little dumb.

personajes.name: Pompompurin
personajes.description: Pompompurin loves pudin, in all ways. He loves the phrase Let's go out! but hatesStay. Friends with anyone.

personajes.name: Tuxedosam
personajes.description: Tuxedosam is a Sanrio character known for his dapper appearance and love for all things stylish, enjoys collecting bowties.

personajes.name: Shirokuma
personajes.description: Based on the idea of finding comfort in the small corners of everyday life, and dislikes cold.

personajes.name: Pandapple
personajes.description: He has a round, apple-shaped head with a panda's face and ears. As he says, an apple a day keeps the doctor away.

personajes.name: Gudetama
personajes.description: He is an anthropomorphic egg yolk with a round head and a small, white shell, always lacking energy.

personajes.name: Aggretsuko
personajes.description: She is a red panda who works in an office job and has a secret passion for heavy metal karaoke.

personajes.name: Hangyodon
personajes.description: known for his unique appearance, a fish with legs and toothy grin. Hangyodon is often portrayed as mischievous and enjoys making people laugh.

personajes.name: Dear Daniel
personajes.description: Hello Kitty's childhood friend and love interest. Dear Daniel enjoys playing guitar, drawing, and spending time with his friend.
